{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/6353","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/6353/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/6353/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/6353/events","html_url":"https://github.com/vuejs/vue/issues/6353","id":249762997,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyNDk3NjI5OTc=","number":6353,"title":"[SSR] context.styles is undefined when `runInNewContext !== true`","user":{"login":"nekuz0r","id":474232,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ3NDIzMg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/474232?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r","html_url":"https://github.com/nekuz0r","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nekuz0r/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2017-08-11T22:31:07Z","updated_at":"2017-09-13T04:32:14Z","closed_at":"2017-09-13T04:32:14Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Version\r\n2.4.2\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://github.com/nekuz0r/vuejs-ssr-styles-issue](https://github.com/nekuz0r/vuejs-ssr-styles-issue)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n```shell\r\nnpm run build\r\nnpm run start\r\n```\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n`context.styles` to be defined\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n`context.styles` is `undefined` when `runInNewContext` is equal `false` or `'once'`\r\n\r\n---\r\ncontext.styles getter is not set on the new context created when\r\n`runInNewContext` is equal to `false` or `once`.\r\n\r\n`vue-style-loader` is defining a getter for `context.styles` property\r\n(https://github.com/vuejs/vue-style-loader/blob/master/lib/addStylesServer.js#L9)\r\n\r\nWhen `runInNewContext` is `false` or `once`, VueJS is copying the `_styles`\r\nproperty in `userContext` from `initialContext` but the `styles` getter is not.\r\n(https://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/8ff77a243cae0627a651fe852a6c07f7bcfce2a3/src/server/bundle-renderer/create-bundle-runner.js#L131)\r\n\r\nAdding the following line after that one fixes the issue\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nObject.defineProperty(userContext, 'styles',\r\n  Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(initialContext, 'styles')\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->","closed_by":{"login":"yyx990803","id":499550,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5OTU1MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/499550?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803","html_url":"https://github.com/yyx990803","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx